		{
			"name": "Evade the Undead",
			"type": "action",
			"effects": [],
			"system": {
				"_migration": {
					"version": 0.955,
					"previous": {
						"schema": 0.953,
						"foundry": "13.351",
						"system": "7.11.2"
					}
				},
				"description": {
					"value": "<section class=\"skill\"><p>While exploring the ruins of Yua's Hope, you move from one location to another while evading the undead that roam the town. Attempt a @Check[type:stealth|dc:10|traits:action:sneak,secret,action:evade-the-undead] check to @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Item.VMozDqMMuK5kpoX4]{Sneak} past the undead or a @Check[type:acrobatics|dc:13|traits:action:evade-the-undead] or @Check[type:athletics|dc:13|traits:action:evade-the-undead] to move so quickly that the undead lose track of your position. Alternatively, you can attempt a @Check[type:society|dc:15|traits:action:recall-knowledge,secret,action:evade-the-undead] check to @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Item.1OagaWtBpVXExToo]{Recall Knowledge} and plot the most efficient route to your destination.</p><ul class=\"outcomes\"><li><strong>Critical Success</strong>: You gain 1 EP.</li><li><strong>Success</strong>: You don't gain or lose EP.</li><li><strong>Failure</strong>: You lose 1 EP.</li><li><strong>Critical failure</strong>: You lose 2 EP.</li></ul></section>",
					"gm": ""
				},
				"publication": {
					"title": "",
					"authors": "",
					"license": "OGL",
					"remaster": false
				},
				"rules": [
					{
						"key": "Note",
						"outcome": [
							"criticalSuccess"
						],
						"text": "You gain 1 EP.",
						"selector": [
							"check"
						],
						"predicate": [
							"action:evade-the-undead"
						]
					},
					{
						"key": "Note",
						"text": "You don't gain or lose EP.",
						"selector": [
							"check"
						],
						"predicate": [
							"action:evade-the-undead"
						],
						"outcome": [
							"success"
						]
					},
					{
						"key": "Note",
						"text": "You lose 1 EP.",
						"selector": [
							"check"
						],
						"predicate": [
							"action:evade-the-undead"
						],
						"outcome": [
							"failure"
						]
					},
					{
						"key": "Note",
						"text": "You lose 2 EP.",
