	"journal": [
		{
			"name": "Claws of the Tyrant: Addons",
			"pages": [
				{
					"name": "Claws of the Tyrant: Addons",
					"type": "text",
					"text": {
						"content": "<p class=\"bio center\">by Chasarooni</p><section class=\"description\"><p>Hi |˶˙ᵕ˙ )ﾉﾞ, this is the module author. I put this together as a collection of miscellaneous resources I found helpful, as well as any maps etc. that I made along the way so the work isn't lost, I hope you enjoy them, and enjoy this Adventure!</p></section><h3>Module Contents</h3><p>Look at the following sections for more information on what specifically is included.</p><ul><li><p>@UUID[JournalEntry.ntwh8NNYToNZNUVq.JournalEntryPage.TncFN3HfVIpIk59L]{1. Gravelands Survivors}</p></li><li><p>@UUID[JournalEntry.ntwh8NNYToNZNUVq.JournalEntryPage.B1fogQPE8sjY5Qjh]{2. Ashes for Ozem}</p></li><li><p>@UUID[JournalEntry.ntwh8NNYToNZNUVq.JournalEntryPage.kWKbOhCv7Mjxadbr]{3. Of Blood and Faith}</p></li></ul>",
						"format": 1
					},
					"title": {
						"level": 1,
						"show": true
					},
					"_id": "33PzIs2xeNtEzGXd",
					"system": {},
					"image": {},
					"video": {
						"controls": true,
						"volume": 0.5
					},
					"src": null,
					"category": null,
					"sort": 100000,
					"flags": {},
					"_stats": {
						"compendiumSource": null,
						"duplicateSource": null,
						"exportSource": null,
						"coreVersion": "13.351",
						"systemId": "pf2e",
						"systemVersion": "7.7.4",
						"lastModifiedBy": "NwwCO5XwERuXrIdd",
						"modifiedTime": 1764704575214
					},
					"ownership": {
						"default": -1
					}
				},
				{
					"sort": 106250,
					"name": "1. Gravelands Survivors",
					"type": "text",
					"_id": "TncFN3HfVIpIk59L",
					"system": {},
					"title": {
						"show": true,
						"level": 2
					},
					"image": {},
					"text": {
						"format": 1,
						"content": "<aside><h3>Resources</h3><p>This is a summary of the resources included in Addons for each section of the Adventure</p></aside><article class=\"blockgroup\"><section class=\"block\"><h3>@UUID[JournalEntry.E7pPpCO9yKvEJH9Z.JournalEntryPage.LUrawCr6IwG4hg95]{Preparing for Farewell}</h3><p>Added some maps to help illustrate the scenes for the early events</p><ul><li><p>@UUID[Compendium.claws-of-the-tyrant-addons.claws-of-the-tyrant-addons-maps.Scene.s1IrAOohrVxXuAzA]{Event 1: Unknown Epitaph}</p></li><li><p>@UUID[Compendium.claws-of-the-tyrant-addons.claws-of-the-tyrant-addons-maps.Scene.dXgvX8G980HbbCws]{Event 2: Work Continues}</p></li><li><p>@UUID[Compendium.claws-of-the-tyrant-addons.claws-of-the-tyrant-addons-maps.Scene.bwNLCb6FTHJAnbKT]{Event 3: Preparing the Body}</p></li><li><p>@UUID[Compendium.claws-of-the-tyrant-addons.claws-of-the-tyrant-addons-maps.Scene.MTyXPofYNUuWkq4v]{Event 4: A Funeral Dirge}</p></li></ul></section><section class=\"block\"><h3>@UUID[JournalEntry.E7pPpCO9yKvEJH9Z.JournalEntryPage.Yk6QotH2TPPC2e4Z]{Yua's Hope}</h3><p>Included the @UUID[Item.o0Dy04c8xUi4fIf9]{Evade the Undead} exploration action to simplify having players roll for it while exploring Yua's Hope.</p><p>Also a @UUID[JournalEntry.ntwh8NNYToNZNUVq.JournalEntryPage.IQG2zLulF99TdI4F]{Map of Yua's Hope} to serve as a guide for the players (based on their memories of the town and its layout)</p></section><section class=\"block\"><h3>@UUID[JournalEntry.q09cHXJPCUX6TluO.JournalEntryPage.DeALWKnwYbayA4Ag]{The March to Vellumis}</h3><p>Thanks to the lovely, <em><strong>@Icarus</strong></em>, included a map to illustrate the route to Vellumis.</p><ul><li><p>@UUID[Compendium.claws-of-the-tyrant-addons.claws-of-the-tyrant-addons-maps.Scene.z78KUiOJBV4Xoa0Z]{Road to Vellumis}</p></li></ul><p>Additionally here is the image with and without the paths</p><aside class=\"flex50 left\"><img width=\"256\" src=\"modules/claws-of-the-tyrant-addons/assets/maps/VellumisMap-1300x1100-GridScale_8.webp\" /><h3>With Paths</h3></aside><aside class=\"flex50 right\"><img width=\"256\" src=\"modules/claws-of-the-tyrant-addons/assets/maps/VellumisMap-1300x1100-GridScale_8-NoPaths.webp\" /><h3>No Paths</h3></aside></section></article>"
					},
